<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>{{subject}}</title>
        <style>
            * {
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
                box-sizing: border-box;
            }

            body {
                font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
                line-height: 1.6;
                color: #333;
                background-color: #f8fafc;
            }

            .email-container {
                max-width: 600px;
                margin: 0 auto;
                background-color: #ffffff;
                border-radius: 12px;
                overflow: hidden;
                box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
            }

            .header {
                background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
                color: white;
                padding: 40px 30px;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .header h1 {
                font-size: 28px;
                font-weight: 700;
                margin-bottom: 8px;
            }

            .header p {
                font-size: 16px;
                opacity: 0.9;
            }

            .content {
                padding: 40px 30px;
            }

            .content h2 {
                color: #1f2937;
                font-size: 24px;
                font-weight: 600;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .content p {
                color: #4b5563;
                font-size: 16px;
                margin-bottom: 16px;
            }

            .button {
                display: inline-block;
                background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
                color: white;
                text-decoration: none;
                padding: 12px 24px;
                border-radius: 8px;
                font-weight: 600;
                margin: 20px 0;
                transition: transform 0.2s ease;
            }

            .button:hover {
                transform: translateY(-2px);
            }

            .info-card {
                background-color: #f8fafc;
                border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
                border-radius: 8px;
                padding: 20px;
                margin: 20px 0;
            }

            .info-row {
                display: flex;
                justify-content: space-between;
                align-items: center;
                padding: 8px 0;
                border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            }

            .info-row:last-child {
                border-bottom: none;
            }

            .info-label {
                font-weight: 600;
                color: #374151;
            }

            .info-value {
                color: #6b7280;
            }

            .footer {
                background-color: #f8fafc;
                padding: 30px;
                text-align: center;
                border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            }

            .footer p {
                color: #6b7280;
                font-size: 14px;
                margin-bottom: 8px;
            }

            .social-links {
                margin-top: 20px;
            }

            .social-links a {
                display: inline-block;
                margin: 0 8px;
                color: #6b7280;
                text-decoration: none;
            }

            @media (max-width: 600px) {
                .email-container {
                    margin: 0;
                    border-radius: 0;
                }

                .header,
                .content,
                .footer {
                    padding: 20px;
                }

                .header h1 {
                    font-size: 24px;
                }

                .content h2 {
                    font-size: 20px;
                }
            }
        </style>
    </head>

    <body>
        <div class="email-container">
            <div class="header">
                <h1>{{companyName}}</h1>
                <p>{{companyTagline}}</p>
            </div>

            <div class="content">
                <h2>üéâ Welcome to {{companyName}}!</h2>

                <p>Hi {{customerName}},</p>

                <p>Welcome aboard! We're thrilled to have you join the {{companyName}} community. You're now part of
                    thousands of
                    satisfied customers who trust us for their needs.</p>

                <div
                    style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; border-radius: 12px; padding: 30px; text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                    <h3 style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px;">üéÅ Welcome Gift</h3>
                    <p style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Get <strong>{{discountPercentage}}% off</strong>
                        your first order!
                    </p>
                    <p style="font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.9;">Use code: <strong>{{welcomeCode}}</strong></p>
                </div>

                <h3 style="color: #1f2937; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; margin: 30px 0 20px 0;">üöÄ Getting Started
                </h3>

                <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin: 20px 0;">
                    <div
                        style="background-color: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
                        <div style="font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px;">üõçÔ∏è</div>
                        <h4 style="color: #1f2937; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px;">Browse
                            Products</h4>
                        <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">Explore our wide selection of products</p>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        style="background-color: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
                        <div style="font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px;">üë§</div>
                        <h4 style="color: #1f2937; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px;">Complete
                            Profile</h4>
                        <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">Add your shipping and payment info</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                    <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">Start Shopping</a>
                </div>

                <div
                    style="background-color: #f0f9ff; border: 1px solid #0ea5e9; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 30px 0;">
                    <h3 style="color: #0c4a6e; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;">üí° Pro Tips</h3>
                    <ul style="color: #0c4a6e; font-size: 14px; padding-left: 20px;">
                        <li>Save your favorite items to your wishlist</li>
                        <li>Enable notifications for order updates</li>
                        <li>Follow us on social media for exclusive deals</li>
                        <li>Check out our customer reviews before buying</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <p>If you have any questions or need help getting started, our support team is here to help. Just reply
                    to this email or
                    contact us through our website.</p>

                <p>Happy shopping!<br>The {{companyName}} Team</p>
            </div>

            <div class="footer">
                <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
                <p>{{companyAddress}}</p>
                <div class="social-links">
                    <a href="{{websiteUrl}}">Website</a>
                    <a href="{{supportEmail}}">Support</a>
                    <a href="{{privacyUrl}}">Privacy Policy</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>

</html>